trans-unit.source: When a script reference is rendered, the ScriptReferenceEventArgs object contains the <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptReference> object that is defined in the <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager> instance.
trans-unit.target: Quando uma referência de script é composta, o objeto de ScriptReferenceEventArgs contém o <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptReference>objeto que está definido a <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager>instância.</xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager> </xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptReference>

trans-unit.source: You can create an event handler for the <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager.ResolveScriptReference> event to check the <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptReference> object and modify it as needed.
trans-unit.target: Pode criar um processador de eventos para o <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager.ResolveScriptReference>evento para verificar o <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptReference>objeto e modificá-lo conforme necessário.</xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptReference> </xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager.ResolveScriptReference>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.ScriptReference"></xref> object that contains the client script referenced on the Web page.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.ScriptReference"> </xref> objeto que contém o script de cliente referenciado na página Web.
